text:
A lot of makeshift stalls selling kueh, snacks, clothing, pants, shoes,
slippers, toys, mobile/hair/home accessories, bedsheets, etc. They are open around 8 am till 12 noon and some till 2 pm. There are 3 shops selling fruits & 1 shop selling fruits & vegetables. To me, this is the best place to shop in Bukit Panjang area.

Itâ€™s nice walk through the alleyway, you get to see and buy fruits and daily groceries. Every morning there is like a morning bazaar along the pathway. Enjoy shopping and buying at this atmosphere. Come and experience this morning vibrancy. Evening is quiet but you can get wonderful deals of fruits to pick up .

A neighborhood market with many household needs, a few fruit stalls, hardware shops, clinics, dentals, etc...

There is also a hawker center nearby.
Popular for fruits markets place,  fruits prices are cheaper. Seasonal tropical fruits can be found here. A place having a village vibe .
Many shops and stalls.. great place for grocery shopping!
